7.
The Japanese love robotic pets and many prefer robotic companions their real live companion.
 Because to care these Pets are much easier, the main target audience of such devices are children.
 Adults believe that the robot dog will fully satisfy the need of kids in love and devotion on the one hand,
  and does not require them (adults), whether spiritual or temporal costs. The market continues to develop and sell new toys.
  High-tech toy has high value because of what the dog is not available to anyone interested.